    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is a solid performer that\u2019s ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest signs of use and age both inside and out, it remains a functional and steady choice for your daily needs. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a reliable vehicle at a very accessible price point!",
